import pyautogui
import time
import uiautomation as auto

try:
    auto.uiautomation.SetGlobalSearchTimeout(10)
    desktop = auto.GetRootControl()
    # Open Start menu
    pyautogui.hotkey('win')
    time.sleep(0.5)
    # Type WhatsApp
    pyautogui.typewrite('whatsapp', interval=0.05)
    time.sleep(0.5)
    # Press Enter to launch
    pyautogui.press('enter')
    time.sleep(2)
    # Verify WhatsApp window appears
    whatsapp = desktop.WindowControl(searchDepth=2, ClassName='Chrome_WidgetWin_1')
    if not whatsapp.Exists(5):
        raise Exception("WhatsApp window not detected")
    print("EXECUTION_SUCCESS")
except Exception as e:
    print("FAILED:", str(e))
